# LJC Accounting App Stack

## Layout
- Backend: `server.js`, `routes/`, `lib/`, `config/database.js`, SQLite at `db/accounting.db`
- Frontend: `frontend/src/` (React + MUI + Vite) → build to `frontend/dist/`
- Integration/loan servicing hooks: `integration/`

## Launchers (do not regress)
- **Silent:** `START-APP.bat` → `Launch_LJC_AI_Accounting.vbs` (no console, opens browser)
- **Debug:** `START-APP-Visible.bat` (console + pause)
- Server port **3000**; health check at `/health`; logs in `logs/server.log`

## API & auth
- JWT auth middleware on protected routes; demo user documented in README.
- Keep CORS/dev vs prod behavior in `server.js` — don't widen production CORS casually.

## When adding features
- Match existing route patterns and SQLite query style in sibling files.
- Update README or `00-READ-ME-FIRST.txt` only when Jerry asks or launch behavior changes.
- Verify: `npm start` or silent launcher after non-trivial changes.
